data.description: Custom Built home with open spacious lay out. New energy efficient windows and doors, new AC just installed this summer. Roof less than five years old. This three bedroom two bath has new flooring throughout. Conveniently located less than five miles from Colleton Medical Center and only two miles from Colleton County High School. Quiet rural neighborhood with NO HOA and no restrictions! Bring your pets they will love the fenced in back yard!*** Motivated seller is offering $5,000 credit toward interest rate buy down with preferred lender! Seller to make no repairs it is being sold as is.
